name: Leopard Print Photo Birthday Invitation - Printable Card
description:
Our custom made designs are the perfect way to make any card you need unique and attention getting! All of our listings are for digital files. They can be customized to fit a 5x7 or 4x6 size, as well as to fit your color scheme.

------------------------------------------

How To Order:

1. Purchase the design of you choice and pay via paypal.


2. Email the following information to:
akissofthis [!at] hotmail.com

*Name of person party is in honor of
*Age
*Party Date / Time
*Party Location
*RSVP details
*Whether you would prefer a 5x7 or 4x6 size
*Any other information you would like included on card
*Photo you would like on card


3. Within 24 hours you will receive a proof via email response. Please review the proof and let me know if you would like any revisions made to it.


4.Once you have approved the final proof, the watermark will be removed and you will then be emailed the high resolution copy of your card.


5. Time to print! You can either print your cards from your home printer, or upload them to your preferred photo printing company. (Walmart, Walgreens, Staples etc)

------------------------------------------

Please Note:
All listings in our shop are for the digital file only. You will receive an email with your product.
